                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-124" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH COLTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the bar-maid. I took the shirt from Smith—Hale was standing at the counter all the time, and the basket was on the floor close by it—I cannot say whether Smith might have taken it without Hale knowing it.</p>
